<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>여행 상세</title>
  
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="detail-body" style="font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; background-color: #faf9f1; margin: 0;">
  <header class="top-header" style="height: 50px; background-color: #005eff; color: #FFFFFF; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 10px 30px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);">
    <div class="header-left">
      <a href="/home" class="logo" style="display: flex; align-items: center; text-decoration: none; color: #ffffff; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">
          <i class="fas fa-plane-departure"></i> 
          <span class="logo-text" style="padding-left: 10px;">Travel</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="header-right" style="display: flex; gap: 10px;">
      <button class="header-btn back-btn" style="background-color: #ffffff; color: #005eff; border: none; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;" onclick="history.back()">
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> 
          <span>이전</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="bg-icon" style="position: absolute; bottom: -400px; right: 10px; font-size: 1500px; color: #005eff; opacity: 0.1; transform: rotate(210deg); pointer-events: none; z-index: -1;">
      <i class="fas fa-plane"></i>
  </div>

  <main class="detail-container board-layout" style="max-width: 940px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 28px 16px 56px;">
    <section class="board-article" style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 18px 40px -24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.25); padding: 28px;">
      <header class="board-head" style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 16px;">
        <div class="board-title">
          <h1 style="margin: 4px 0 8px; font-size: 28px; color: #000000; background-color: #005eff; padding: 20px 30px; border-radius: 15px;">제주도 여행</h1>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="board-tags" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; padding: 16px 0 10px;">
        <span class="pill" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 999px; background: #eef2ff; color: #4338ca; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;">
          <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>제주도
        </span>
        <span class="pill" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 999px; background: #eef2ff; color: #4338ca; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;">
          <i class="fas fa-users"></i>4명
        </span>
        <span class="pill" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 999px; background: #eef2ff; color: #4338ca; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;">
          <i class="fas fa-wallet"></i>100만원
        </span>
      </div>

      <article class="board-body" style="margin-top: 18px; padding: 16px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px;">
        <h3 class="section-title" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 16px; color: #0f172a;">
          <i class="fas fa-info-circle" style="color: #1d4ed8;"></i>상세 내용
        </h3>
        <p class="detail-text" style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; color: #334155; white-space: pre-line;">제주도에서 힐링하고 맛집 탐방하는 3박 4일 여행을 계획하고 있습니다. 함께 가실 분 찾습니다!</p>
        <div class="board-meta footer-meta" style="display: flex; gap: 12px; color: #0f172a; font-size: 14px; justify-content: flex-end; margin-top: 12px;">
          <span><i class="fas fa-user" style="margin-right: 6px;"></i>김여행</span>
          <span><i class="far fa-clock" style="margin-right: 6px;"></i>2025. 12. 2. PM 11:49:43</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <section class="board-body route-body" style="margin-top: 18px; padding: 16px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px;">
        <h3 class="section-title" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 16px; color: #0f172a;">
          <i class="fas fa-route" style="color: #1d4ed8;"></i>방문지
        </h3>
        <div class="tag-wrap" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px;">
          <span class="tag" style="display: inline-flex; padding: 6px 10px; border-radius: 8px; background: #e2e8f0; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;">#성산일출봉</span>
          <span class="tag" style="display: inline-flex; padding: 6px 10px; border-radius: 8px; background: #e2e8f0; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;">#우도</span>
          <span class="tag" style="display: inline-flex; padding: 6px 10px; border-radius: 8px; background: #e2e8f0; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;">#협재해수욕장</span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
